This hotel is part of the Hilton group, but doesn't meet Hilton standards.	This hotel was beautiful, new and well kept, but the "service" provided by the staff and the management of this hotel fell well below Hilton standards.	The location sells the hotel, but the staff, cleanliness, and service were all top notch - even above Hilton's generally good standards.	One of the attractions of staying at a Hilton is expecting a standard level of customer service and satisfaction.	This is definitely one of Hilton standard hotel.	I have been in many hotels where the chair is a standard upholstered chair and the height is really not suitable for business travellers.